title: Braum Skin Idea

embed.description: I listened to the John Cena Prank Call and used the audio for the beginning, and used various other sounds from YouTube in it. I wanted this as a ringtone cuz I thought it was hilarious, but nobody had the explosion sound included without the rapping & yelling, so I decided to put something together.

body:
Braum needs a new skin... 

and we will call it...

JOHN CENA!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

replies.body: Tired and overused memes are tired and overused.
